      "author": "fanxin199",
      "description": "## DeepL Translate Selection v1.0.0\r\n\r\nInitial release 🎉\r\n\r\n### Features\r\n- 🖱️ Right-click to translate selected text using DeepL API\r\n- 🌐 Auto-detects Chinese↔English direction\r\n- 📋 Three output options: Insert Below, Replace Selection, Copy\r\n- 🔑 Supports both DeepL Free and Pro API keys\r\n- 🧠 Uses DeepL's quality_optimized model\r\n\r\n### Installation\r\n1. Download [main.js](cci:7://file:///d:/obsidian_writing/.obsidian/plugins/deepl-translate-selection/main.js:0:0-0:0), [manifest.json](cci:7://file:///H:/software_build/deepl-translate-selection/manifest.json:0:0-0:0), and [styles.css](cci:7://file:///d:/obsidian_writing/.obsidian/plugins/deepl-translate-selection/styles.css:0:0-0:0) below\r\n2. Create folder `deepl-translate-selection` in your vault's `.obsidian/plugins/`\r\n3. Place the 3 files inside, restart Obsidian and enable the plugin\r\n",
